============================================
 * Workflow :
 * ============================================
 * init_data() => the data passed from arguments
 * put_table()
 *  |-> create_philosophers(table)
 *  |-> create_forks(table)
 * serve_dinner(table)
 *  |-> check_philosophers_action(philos, forks)
 *  |----> can_eat(philo)
 *  |----> set_new_state(philo)
 *  |----------> eating
 *  |----------> sleeping
 *  |----------> thinking
 *  |----------> died
 *  |----> all_have_eat_enough()
 *  |----> has_died()
 *  |--------> end_dinner()

